# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
#  DEPARTMENT EMAIL ROUTING
#  Each alert type sends to the relevant department(s).
#  You can add multiple emails separated by commas.
#
#  EMAIL_DEPT_FIRE    → receives: fire_hazard alerts
#  EMAIL_DEPT_POLICE  → receives: collision, overcrowding, fire_hazard alerts
#  EMAIL_DEPT_MEDICAL → receives: collision, medical_emergency alerts
#  EMAIL_DEPT_MUNICIPAL → receives: littering, garbage_hotspot alerts
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
EMAIL_DEPT_FIRE=firedept.demo@gmail.com
EMAIL_DEPT_POLICE=policedeptment.demo@gmail.com
EMAIL_DEPT_MEDICAL=medicaldept.demo@gmail.com
EMAIL_DEPT_MUNICIPAL=municipaldept.demo@gmail.com

# Fallback: if a department key is not set, alert goes to all of these
